 bindings = <
 //╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷         ╷
              &kp Q     &kp W     &kp F     &kp P     &kp G                   &kp J     &kp L     &kp U     &kp Y     &kp SEMI
    &kp TAB   &hm LSHFT A   &kp R  &kp S    &kp T     &kp D                    &kp H     &kp N     &kp E     &kp I     &hm RSHFT O     &kp SQT
&kp ESC &kp Z    &kp X     &kp C     &kp V     &kp B     &trans     &trans    &kp K     &kp M     &kp COMMA &kp DOT   &slash_ret  &scln_ret
                            &mt LALT RET   &TT_NUMBERS   &mt LCTRL BSPC &trans   &trans  &lt NAV SPACE   &mo SYMBOLS &mt RALT RGUI    
